    • Method Detail

      • addEgo

        public void addEgo(Id id)
        Description copied from interface: SocialNetwork
        Must be called before adding ties. This allows to make sure that isolated agents (without social contacts) are identified as such in the network. This is necessary for analysing the topology of the network, but also for more safety in simulation (fail if the social network does not cover the whole population).
        Specified by:
